00:17:37,730 --> 00:17:39,870
Jangan malu karena kau lemah.

224
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:43,870
Tapi malulah,
kalau kau tak berubah!

225
00:17:46,610 --> 00:17:48,050
Benar.

226
00:17:49,150 --> 00:17:52,100
Bukankah dia yang
membuktikannya padaku?

227
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:57,310
Kalau dia bisa, aku juga bisa...

228
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:03,100
...jadi lebih kuat!

229
00:18:08,370 --> 00:18:09,780
Kakak!

230
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:17,190
Matilah kalian seperti para pecundang!

231
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:25,500
Oh, tidak!

232
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:27,460
Aku takkan sempat!

233
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,710
Siapa kau?

234
00:18:39,710 --> 00:18:40,840
Noelle!

235
00:18:40,840 --> 00:18:43,100
Apa yang kaulakukan, Asta Bego?

236
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:45,460
Aku tak bisa berdiam
diri saja lihat semua ini.

237
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:48,440
Aku akan membantumu, jadi kau
harus berterima kasih padaku!

238
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,270
Ya!

239
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:52,470
Kalau kau bisa bergerak bebas,
dia takkan bisa hentikanmu.

240
00:18:52,470 --> 00:18:53,580
Majulah!

241
00:18:54,570 --> 00:18:56,440
Sepertinya kau sudah
kembali normal.

242
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:58,860
Siapa juga yang bersedih?

243
00:18:58,860 --> 00:19:00,910
Dasar bocah-bocah sialan!

244
00:19:04,490 --> 00:19:06,870
Jangan sombong dulu!

245
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:14,660
Aku akan membantumu, Rivalku!

246
00:19:14,660 --> 00:19:17,500
Habisi si pecundang sialan itu!

247
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:20,220
Kerahkan seluruh kekuatanmu!

248
00:19:20,690 --> 00:19:24,140
Anu, terima kasih banyak!

249
00:19:24,140 --> 00:19:25,850
Kau tak perlu berterima kasih padaku!

250
00:19:25,850 --> 00:19:30,550
Dan juga, sejak awal aku
memang berniat lakukan hal itu!

251
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:48,120
Belum, masih belum!

252
00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:53,120
Waduh.

253
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:57,340
Berhasil!

254
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:58,960
Kakak!

255
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:02,630
Gaya bertarungmu sangat
berbeda dengan para penyihir lain!

256
00:20:02,730 --> 00:20:04,420
Kau memang orang yang menarik!

257
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:17,690
Jangan biarkan serangan konyol
seperti itu kalahkanmu, Jimmy!

258
00:20:18,110 --> 00:20:19,660
Hoi, Jimmy!

259
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:21,240
Hentikan ocehanmu!

260
00:20:21,610 --> 00:20:24,240
Ayo majulah dan hadapi aku!

261
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:29,940
Jangan sombong dulu, Bocah Sialan!

262
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:33,100
Majulah, Alfred!

263
00:20:40,650 --> 00:20:43,760
Nomor 2, Alfred.

264
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:48,710
Majulah, Alfred!

265
00:21:10,580 --> 00:21:11,580
Asta.

266
00:22:44,780 --> 00:22:47,340
Semanggi Kerdil!

267
00:22:48,690 --> 00:22:49,500
Ra!

268
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:53,170
Halo.

269
00:22:53,170 --> 00:22:54,410
Halo.

270
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:56,180
Namaku Asta,
senang bertemu denganmu.

271
00:22:56,600 --> 00:23:00,110
Anu, kau masih belum
sebutkan namamu.

272
00:23:00,110 --> 00:23:02,190
Bisakah kau beri tahu namamu?

273
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:04,940
Hai, namaku Rades.
(Hai, ore no namae wa Rades desu.)

274
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,690
Radesdesu?

275
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:07,450
Begitu, ya.

276
00:23:07,450 --> 00:23:09,700
Kau berasal dari mana, Radesdesu?

277
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:12,940
Bukan Radesdesu,
tak perlu pakai desu-nya.

278
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:14,360
Tak perlu pakai desu-nya?

279
00:23:14,460 --> 00:23:15,840
Jadi, namamu Ra, ya?

280
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:16,970
Siapa yang kau panggil Ra?

281
00:23:16,970 --> 00:23:18,520
Habisnya, tadi katanya
tak pakai desu?

282
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:21,500
Namaku Rades desu,
maksudku jangan pakai "desu."

283
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:23,460
Radesdesu, tapi jangan pakai "desu".

284
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:26,150
Jadi, kalau desu-nya tak dipakai...

285
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:27,100
Hanya ada Ra, 'kan?

286
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:30,540
Sudah kubilang kau salah,
namaku Rades!

287
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,510
Rades!

288
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:37,990
Kau harus ingat itu, Bocah Sialan!

289
00:23:39,530 --> 00:23:43,020
Kesatria Sihir bukanlah tandinganku.

290
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:45,770
Aku, Rades, adalah yang terkuat!

